{"tid":422075,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聲稱男子涉刑事案索款兩萬　一名警員涉勒索被捕","createTime":"2017-10-02T18:06:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T00:29:35.000Z","uid":30647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"701fe90ef70e0c6a8ba5283f522ba2bf028d2215","tid":422075,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T18:06:05.000Z","msg":"聲稱男子涉刑事案索款兩萬　一名警員涉勒索被捕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名警員涉嫌勒索及盜竊被捕，現時已被停職。<br />\n<br />\n涉案49歲男警員據報早前向一名男子聲稱他涉及一宗刑事案件，要求事主給予他兩萬元，以換取不追究案件。事主將一萬元交給這名警員，其後感到可疑於是報案，警方昨日在機場將涉案警員拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">警方表示警隊非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1357046-20171003.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1357046-20171003.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=odyUmP8p2X5HJDa9TshqBZUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=bf322b8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1357046-20171003.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2edbeaac\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1357046-20171003.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"90cd023b5dd57f45b141db7ebc9ea02f338dad92","tid":422075,"uid":25179,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T18:45:37.000Z","msg":"次次都講紅字段野當正視左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fba2de1d875c4bc5635b90ba75a1e24767250d","tid":422075,"uid":83097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T23:25:59.000Z","msg":"普通市民同藍衫狗既犯罪率相比根本就係巴士對保時捷<br />\n無得比"},{"pid":"431d3b8c50448f6e2345462839eec7d270ea4fb9","tid":422075,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T23:27:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>次次都講紅字段野當正視左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識背啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class